{"tid":1744340,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"<曱甴王地產帝國>家門不幸","createTime":"2019-11-21T16:06:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-02T16:51:16.000Z","uid":265814,"like":28,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"e26e27e2bf34318c208305d83ea0b0549a9ca04f","tid":1744340,"uid":265814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T16:06:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />李氏力場。<br />\n被譽為最強黃絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">又「黃台之瓜」、「網開一面」</span>、又捐錢打救零售飲食業，可惜<strong>家門不幸</strong>，出左個要「<strong>殺滅曱甴</strong>」嘅員工，<span style=\"font-size: large;\">條友係長實樓盤公關要員</span>，佢唔單止盲撐警、當大學生危急關頭時，<span style=\"font-size: large;\">仲大大聲話要殺滅<span style=\"color: red;\">「<strong>曱甴</strong>」</span>、同鬧記者係<span style=\"color: red;\">「<strong>黑媒</strong>」</span>，睇黎佢想連自己老闆都滅殺</span>。 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">聽聞佢同d狗官一樣全家攞外國passport，正正係no stake in HK la</span>，咁一齊幫下手推薦佢返大灣區發展！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nP.S. P牌仔推唔到，麻煩幫推清算師，推到俾加拿大領事館知道<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">（因為絲打冇連登，所以代post）<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e6hJ1M0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe6hJ1M0.jpg&h=cdc462d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XAxYQFh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXAxYQFh.jpg&h=f8121103&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tC89cTC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtC89cTC.jpg&h=55442a87&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qVcU8rY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2